decks.notes: The deck focuses on overwhelming the opponent with a swarm of small creatures while utilizing disruptive spells and protective effects to maintain board presence. Isamaru, Hound of Konda serves as a fast and efficient aggressive commander, supported by a variety of low-cost creatures like Giver of Runes, Leonin Arbiter, and Mirran Crusader. Cards like Swords to Plowshares and Skyclave Apparition provide removal options, while Thalia, Guardian of Thraben and Archon of Emeria disrupt opponents' strategies. The deck also includes equipment like Umezawa's Jitte and Stoneforge Mystic to pump up creatures and provide additional benefits. Lands like Castle Ardenvale and Eiganjo Castle help to generate tokens and protect key creatures, while White Plume Adventurer and Recruiter of the Guard offer card advantage and flexibility.
